    - target: {fileID: 8125658855693965992, guid: bc305532fc68e7f41992aa5407724919, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "<b>Left Click</b> \u2192 Fill a tile.\n\n<b>Right Click</b> \u2192
        Block a tile.\n\n<b>Numbers</b> show how many consecutive filled tiles are
        in each row or column. \"For example: <b>1 2</b> means there is a block of
        <b>1 filled tile</b>,  followed by <b>at least one empty tile</b>, and then
        a block of <b>2 filled tiles</b>.\"\n\nSolve all numbers correctly to reveal
        the hidden picture!"
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
